  "keyFeatures": [
    "Plain C/C++ implementation with no external dependencies",
    "Apple Silicon first-class support via ARM NEON, Metal, and Core ML",
    "NVIDIA GPU acceleration via CUDA and cuBLAS",
    "Vulkan cross-vendor GPU support",
    "Integer quantization for reduced memory footprint",
    "Voice Activity Detection (VAD) with Silero-VAD support",
    "Real-time audio transcription from microphone input",
    "Word-level timestamps and speaker diarization (tinydiarize)",
    "HTTP server with OpenAI-compatible API",
    "Bindings for Go, JavaScript, Java, Ruby, Rust, Python, .NET, and Swift"
  ],
